*******************************
READ ME FOR THE STARTER PROJECT
*******************************
this is a template for any typescript project
The package,json has the following libraries included:
tsc -for typescript compilation
nodemon - for hot loading the code 
Folder structure
----------------
src - has all the source code
.env - has all the config properties
index.ts - is the starter file 

package.json entries
--------------------
scripts block - has dev and build scripts
the build script will need to be executed for transpiling the code to js
the dev script will need to be run as "npm run dev"

dev dependencies block - has nodemon, tsc and ts-node need to be there for the dev

dependencies block - the packages needed for API calls - axios, postman